liberate the people?"Then I heard of guerrilla

00:41:30.079 --> 00:41:36.000
warfare. They said,

00:41:36.000 --> 00:41:42.640
"A

00:41:38.880 --> 00:41:44.800
dangerous Iran is

00:41:42.640 --> 00:41:48.799
an

00:41:44.800 --> 00:41:51.760
unstable

00:41:51.760 --> 00:41:58.160
Iran."It's

00:41:59.760 --> 00:42:02.560
dangerous because of what they have underneath the

00:42:01.920 --> 00:42:04.240
mountain.

