to the point where it was like they weren't

00:42:36.240 --> 00:42:41.520
thinking soundly anymore.

00:42:38.000 --> 00:42:45.520
It was very

00:42:46.880 --> 00:42:50.319
dark,

00:42:48.560 --> 00:42:52.799
like suicide.

00:43:15.520 --> 00:43:22.240
I saw them doing the

00:43:18.880 --> 00:43:26.880
