00:43:22.240 --> 00:43:28.799
But I saw a black weapon—a weapon that

00:43:26.880 --> 00:43:30.560
they've held back underneath the

00:43:28.800 --> 00:43:33.839
mountain that they think nobody

00:43:30.560 --> 00:43:35.680
