00:43:39.359 --> 00:43:46.480
I saw a dark plan with a kamikaze action.

00:43:42.560 --> 00:43:49.119
I

00:43:46.480 --> 00:43:52.560
heard "regime change"again.

00:43:49.119 --> 00:43:55.440
Another regime change is coming.

00:43:52.560 --> 00:43:57.040
I saw the

00:43:55.440 --> 00:43:59.280
