That's why the Lord said, "Pray over Pahlavi,

00:44:04.160 --> 00:44:09.520
Reza

00:44:07.040 --> 00:44:12.480
Pahlavi."Pray

00:44:09.520 --> 00:44:13.759
over this man. I saw him

00:44:12.480 --> 00:44:15.520
because they don't want him to be your

00:44:13.760 --> 00:44:17.200
leader, and they'll have to pray over

