saw him trying to rise up with a proxy

00:44:20.160 --> 00:44:24.799
government.

00:44:21.920 --> 00:44:27.680
I saw a kamikaze action

00:44:24.800 --> 00:44:29.760
with these people, but I

00:44:27.680 --> 00:44:32.078
saw freedom fighters.

00:44:32.079 --> 00:44:36.000
He said freedom

00:44:34.319 --> 00:44:37.520
fighters will try to rise up, and the

