00:44:45.119 --> 00:44:53.200
to dethrone and disarm

00:44:49.680 --> 00:44:56.160
the government and the police

00:44:53.200 --> 00:45:02.118
force.

00:44:56.160 --> 00:45:02.118
I saw an armament of citizens

