that weren't very good, but they were

00:45:19.040 --> 00:45:22.000
in the back of

00:45:20.480 --> 00:45:24.640
these trucks. They were freedom

00:45:22.000 --> 00:45:26.160
fighters with things on their heads, looking

00:45:24.640 --> 00:45:28.720
almost like

00:45:26.160 --> 00:45:30.160
Afghans.

