I heard the word "freedom

00:45:30.160 --> 00:45:38.160
fighters."The

00:45:33.680 --> 00:45:41.040
Lord showed us to

00:45:38.160 --> 00:45:42.960
pray over America, our

00:45:41.040 --> 00:45:44.880
