Then the Lord showed us about Iran.

00:45:44.880 --> 00:45:50.240
They were

00:45:48.640 --> 00:45:51.520
debating "boots on

00:45:50.240 --> 00:45:52.720
the

00:45:51.520 --> 00:45:55.359
ground."Saudi

00:45:52.720 --> 00:45:58.240
Arabia was a big help, and so were

00:45:55.359 --> 00:46:00.720
other nations. Pakistan was

00:45:58.240 --> 00:46:02.399
neutral. They said, "We could

00:46:00.720 --> 00:46:05.439
