00:46:05.440 --> 00:46:10.560
hates us. But Turkey was saying,

00:46:08.400 --> 00:46:13.760
"Hey, we're your friend,"and so

00:46:10.560 --> 00:46:15.680
was Syria. I saw

00:46:13.760 --> 00:46:18.319
certain sectors of people saying, "Listen,

00:46:18.319 --> 00:46:24.240
we will add our supply if we need to."The

00:46:20.400 --> 00:46:27.440
main one was MBS, Mohammed

00:46:24.240 --> 00:46:29.520
bin Salman.

00:46:27.440 --> 00:46:30.400
You might

00:46:29.520 --> 00:46:31.599
say, "Well,

00:46:30.400 --> 00:46:33.440
Brandon, that was a big mess. You

00:46:31.599 --> 00:46:35.520
missed that all the way."We see in

00:46:33.440 --> 00:46:37.839
part. I did the best

00:46:35.520 --> 00:46:40.319
I could; that's what I saw, and I keep

00:46:37.839 --> 00:46:42.960
praying into it.

00:46:40.319 --> 00:46:45.359
We

00:46:42.960 --> 00:46:47.200
never want to be flaky, but we're human.

00:47:01.680 --> 00:47:06.960
I saw battalions

00:47:04.319 --> 00:47:09.119
concerning

00:47:06.960 --> 00:47:10.240
Syria and Iran. A battalion is

00:47:12.720 --> 00:47:16.560
composed of 300 to a

00:47:15.520 --> 00:47:18.880
thousand soldiers.

00:47:16.560 --> 00:47:23.240
I

00:47:23.440 --> 00:47:28.319
saw Oklahoma.

00:47:28.319 --> 00:47:35.920
The Lord said, "Do not

00:47:31.359 --> 00:47:40.000
assume Oklahoma will flip red and

00:47:35.920 --> 00:47:43.920
