00:51:19.359 --> 00:51:25.200
his head that was missed, all

00:51:22.559 --> 00:51:29.200
the attempts to put him in prison,

00:51:25.200 --> 00:51:32.240
the attacks against his family, his Mar-a-Lago

00:51:29.200 --> 00:51:35.279
