00:51:32.240 --> 00:51:40.000
moments led up to nothing; it was all

00:51:35.280 --> 00:51:42.800
hot air. The Save America Act was a

00:51:40.000 --> 00:51:45.680
balloon with a vast void

00:51:42.800 --> 00:51:48.400
that wasn't able to be passed. I saw

00:51:45.680 --> 00:51:50.160
ahead a void, and the Lord said, "Pray

00:51:48.400 --> 00:51:52.800
