00:52:30.400 --> 00:52:35.599
saw these support systems to

00:52:33.119 --> 00:52:38.640
support this if you couldn't get this

00:52:35.599 --> 00:52:40.880
passed. I saw the support system at the

00:52:38.640 --> 00:52:43.920
bottom to help it so it would have

00:52:40.880 --> 00:52:47.280
a little stability. It had three

00:52:43.920 --> 00:52:49.440
major parts splitting off of the

00:52:47.280 --> 00:52:51.680
Save America Act that could be

00:52:49.440 --> 00:52:54.319
implemented and passed, that it had the

00:52:51.680 --> 00:52:57.359
votes for when the whole thing didn't.

00:52:54.319 --> 00:52:59.759
Now, I don't know what that is, but I saw

00:52:57.359 --> 00:53:02.720
support systems and the Lord said, "Focus on

00:52:59.760 --> 00:53:05.359
this.

00:53:02.720 --> 00:53:07.359
Don't waste this time."I saw him

00:53:05.359 --> 00:53:11.279
standing on the steps of the

00:53:07.359 --> 00:53:14.078
ballroom disappointed. It had so

00:53:11.280 --> 00:53:16.960
