00:53:29.040 --> 00:53:34.640
beside it. It looked like

00:53:31.440 --> 00:53:37.599
a whirlwind, and it was outside on the

00:53:34.640 --> 00:53:41.440
lawn of the White House. I

00:53:37.599 --> 00:53:43.920
saw a great storm next to a flag coming.

00:53:41.440 --> 00:53:47.040
I saw an American flag; it was blowing to

00:53:43.920 --> 00:53:50.000
the west—an

00:53:47.040 --> 00:53:53.040
east wind blowing into the west.

00:53:50.000 --> 00:53:56.400
I could see this flag rippling as a

00:53:53.040 --> 00:53:59.359
whirlwind of these three doves going

00:53:56.400 --> 00:54:02.079
down with olive leaves inside of

00:53:59.359 --> 00:54:04.558
this whirlwind circling the White

00:54:02.079 --> 00:54:06.880
House lawn. It was a whirlwind, and

00:54:04.559 --> 00:54:10.240
you could see it, but it looked like the Holy

00:54:06.880 --> 00:54:13.599
Ghost. It wasn't scary. Three doves; they

00:54:10.240 --> 00:54:16.879
were beautiful. The doves were at the top,

00:54:13.599 --> 00:54:19.280
middle, and bottom—three layers of

00:54:16.880 --> 00:54:21.359
doves in a whirlwind turning

00:54:19.280 --> 00:54:23.520
by a flag outside of the White

00:54:21.359 --> 00:54:25.279
House. I saw President Trump

00:54:23.520 --> 00:54:26.960
out there and he was looking out

00:54:25.280 --> 00:54:29.920
across his accomplishments, but he was

00:54:26.960 --> 00:54:31.839
disappointed because he had so much

00:54:29.920 --> 00:54:34.400
he wanted to do that he never got

00:54:31.839 --> 00:54:34.400
done.

00:54:34.880 --> 00:54:39.599
We must pray that we don't have a

00:54:37.760 --> 00:54:42.599
stalemate presidency in the next four

00:54:39.599 --> 00:54:42.599
months.

00:54:42.880 --> 00:54:49.280
We've got to really grasp a hold of this—a

00:54:45.440 --> 00:54:53.119
stalemate presidency

00:54:49.280 --> 00:54:55.839
that would try to come—and his legacy

00:54:53.119 --> 00:54:58.079
of what he has done and all that he has

00:54:55.839 --> 00:55:00.400
fought to get. We fought so hard to get

00:54:58.079 --> 00:55:02.960
him through the voter fraud and all the

00:55:00.400 --> 00:55:06.800
things that we fought for so hard in 2024—"Joe

00:55:02.960 --> 00:55:09.200
Biden too big to rig."I prayed

00:55:06.800 --> 00:55:12.960
more over that than I prayed

00:55:09.200 --> 00:55:16.399
anything. "Too big to rig 2024, too big

00:55:12.960 --> 00:55:17.440
to rig."And it was with Kamala Harris.

00:55:16.400 --> 00:55:18.880
They didn't know what to do because there were

00:55:17.440 --> 00:55:21.200
so many people that showed up on

00:55:18.880 --> 00:55:23.119
that boat as they were all patriots

00:55:21.200 --> 00:55:26.960
coming out.

00:55:23.119 --> 00:55:29.440
I saw a big nothingburger, a big

00:55:26.960 --> 00:55:30.960
hot air balloon. That was what

00:55:29.440 --> 00:55:32.480
he was. "We're going to do this. We're

00:55:30.960 --> 00:55:34.240
going to make America great again. We're

00:55:32.480 --> 00:55:36.800
going to do all that."It came to nothing.

00:55:34.240 --> 00:55:39.520
It was a ballroom.

00:55:36.800 --> 00:55:41.599
As he stood on the steps looking out,

00:55:39.520 --> 00:55:44.559
he had less than two years left and he

00:55:41.599 --> 00:55:46.640
was thinking, "What do I do now?"I saw

00:55:44.559 --> 00:55:48.079
the ballroom and I said, "Is

00:55:46.640 --> 00:55:49.680
this 2027? Is he going to have the

00:55:48.079 --> 00:55:52.319
ballroom built where he can stand on the steps?"I

00:55:49.680 --> 00:55:54.078
have no idea. Is it a metaphor?

00:55:52.319 --> 00:55:57.680
Is it something that I'm seeing? Is it a

00:55:54.079 --> 00:56:00.000
type of shadow? I don't

00:55:57.680 --> 00:56:01.520
know. I just see him standing there,

00:56:00.000 --> 00:56:03.920
and it looked like JD

00:56:01.520 --> 00:56:06.079
Vance was on his right hand.

00:56:03.920 --> 00:56:08.079
He

00:56:06.079 --> 00:56:09.839
had a red tie, white shirt, and

00:56:08.079 --> 00:56:11.760
jacket, and he was standing next

00:56:09.839 --> 00:56:14.799
to him. They were looking out at the

00:56:11.760 --> 00:56:17.359
lawn, and there were some steps, and I was like, "What?"I

00:56:14.799 --> 00:56:21.119
saw the

00:56:17.359 --> 00:56:24.000
legacy of him will be a ballroom.

00:56:21.119 --> 00:56:25.920
I said, "God, no,

00:56:24.000 --> 00:56:28.720
no,

00:56:25.920 --> 00:56:30.319
no.

00:56:28.720 --> 00:56:33.520
I don't really care about a man's

00:56:30.319 --> 00:56:35.599
legacy. I care about America. I care

00:56:33.520 --> 00:56:37.119
about awakening unto God. I care about

00:56:35.599 --> 00:56:38.880
revival."The

00:56:37.119 --> 00:56:41.599
Lord said, "I'm calling one last

00:56:38.880 --> 00:56:45.520
call, one major push for a harvest of souls."I

00:56:41.599 --> 00:56:49.440
know I told you a thousand

00:56:45.520 --> 00:56:51.759
times, even in 2024, I said Trump will not

00:56:49.440 --> 00:56:54.400
save America. The only thing that will

00:56:51.760 --> 00:56:56.559
save America is an awakening unto God.

00:56:54.400 --> 00:57:00.319
I feel like I'm

00:56:56.559 --> 00:57:03.280
a broken record half the time,

00:57:00.319 --> 00:57:05.520
but it's about

00:57:03.280 --> 00:57:07.119
it. The Lord said, as I was looking into

00:57:05.520 --> 00:57:08.960
it, it wasn't about the Christians

00:57:07.119 --> 00:57:10.559
rising up and voting. It was about the

00:57:08.960 --> 00:57:12.319
world—the

00:57:10.559 --> 00:57:15.359
secular

00:57:12.319 --> 00:57:17.680
blue-collar workers, the white-collar—they

00:57:15.359 --> 00:57:19.520
were mad at him.

00:57:17.680 --> 00:57:22.240
I said his approval rating will go

00:57:19.520 --> 00:57:25.440
down to 25%.

00:57:22.240 --> 00:57:29.040
I saw 25% on his approval rating and

00:57:25.440 --> 00:57:31.359
he'll have a stalemate presidency.

